@node I_Installation "IdentifyBB2/Installation"
@prev I_Requirements
@next I_History

               @{FG "highlight"}Installation@{FG "Text"}

     To install all files provided with this archive, simply copy them
     in your favourite directory.
    
     Now, open BLITZLIBS:libnums.bb2 and look at slot #198. If this slot is
     free, well, put identify library here, writing something as:

          #identify=198

     Copy IdentifyBB2/amigalibs/identify.library1 in BLITZLIBS:amigalibs and
     run MakeDefLibs (it should be in BLITZLIBS:).
     
     If your slot is busy, well:

     @{i}- Copy identify.library in your LIBS: drawer
     - Run FDConvert passing identify_lib.fd as parameter.
     - You will be asked for a library number between 1 and 255: insert an
       empty number (look again in BLITZLIBS:libnums.bb2 if you're not sure).
       FDConvert will convert FD file in a BB2 library. It should be found
       in BLITZLIBS:amigalibs/.
     - Now run MakeDefLibs. A new deflibs file will be created.
     @{ui}

     Run BB2...

@endnode

